title: Marvel's "Black Panther" sets new record
text:
Marvel's "Black Panther" sets new record 1:49pm IST - 01:09 
With $631 million in domestic sales, Marvel's ''Black Panther'' becomes the highest-grossing superhero movie in U.S. history. Diane Hodges reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
